            "title": "盤中速報 - 動力-KY(6591)股價拉至漲停，漲停價70.1元，成交7,841張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>動力-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6591:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6591\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6591-TW</a>)15日10:33上漲6.3元，股價漲停報70.1元，委買3,107張，成交7,841張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為散熱風扇。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>動力-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6591:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6591\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6591-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲33.06%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.02%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,158 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,136 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+22 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,200 張</li> <li>融券增減：+450 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
